Coronavirus (CoV) wuxuu ka tirsan yahay Coronaviridae, oo ah koox ka kooban fayrasyo faafa, oo leh RNA iyo hal nooc oo ah.
Noocyada fayraska ee u dhexeeya 26 iyo 32 kilobase oo ka mid ah fayraska RNA waxaa loo yaqaan "CoV" sababtoo ah waxay u muuqdaan kuwo aad u yaryar marka loo eego microscopically.
Sababtoo ah sida ay u kala duwan yihiin, CoVs ma laha hiddo-wadaag hal-halis ah.
Laba qaybood oo ka mid ah saddexda qaybood ee genome-ka ayaa leh laba qaybood oo isbeddelka ah oo loo yaqaan 'reproductive proteinase' (ORF1a iyo ORF1b), kuwaas oo ku salaysan pp1a iyo pp1ab replicase polyprotein.
Polyproteins waxaa sidoo kale loo isticmaalaa in lagu helo borotiinada aan lahayn unugyada 16, kuwaas oo loo yaqaan 'NSP1~16'.
Qaybta dhexe ee hiddaha ee unugyada waxay leedahay ORFs oo ah unugyo proteins ah, oo ay ku jiraan madaxa (S), xuubka (E), jirka (M) iyo nucleoprotein (N).
Waxaa jira tiro badan oo ah noocyada protein-ka ee la xidhiidha hidde-wadaha, sidoo kale waxaa jira tiro badan oo ah noocyada hidda-wadaha CoV-yada.
Iyadoo lagu saleynayo kala duwanaanta heerka borotiinka, CoVs waxay u kala jaban yihiin afar qaybood (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV iyo delta-CoV), kuwaas oo beta-CoVs ay leeyihiin inta badan CoVs waxayna sidoo kale leeyihiin afar qaybood oo asaas u ah (A, B, C iyo D).
