WHO ayaa ku eedaysay dowladda Shiinaha inay ku guul darreysatay inay ka hortagto iyo xakamayso cudurka.
WHO waxay ogaatay kala duwanaanshaha ka dhexeeya cudurka SARS ee 2002-2004, kaas oo ay ku eedeysay dowladda Shiinaha inay tahay mid si khalad ah u fulisay oo ay ku fulisay tallaabooyin ka hortag iyo ka hortag ah, iyo cudurkaas oo dowladda dhexe "ku soo warisay in saddex jeer ay dadku ku dhinteen ka hor inta uusan bilaaban bisha cusub".
Bishii Janaayo 23, si ay uga jawaabto diidmada dowladda dhexe ee ah inay ku soo bandhigeen khatar ku soo wajahan nidaamka daryeelka ee Wuhan, Gauden Galea oo ah agaasimaha WHO ayaa ogaaday in "maanta oo kale, WHO ma aysan sameynin wax horumar ah", waxay ahayd "talaabo muhiim ah oo ay qaadeen si looga hortago in cudurku uu noqdo fayras aad u xun" oo lagu tilmaamay "mid aan horay loo arag taariikhda caafimaadka".
Madaxa WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC ay tahay "mid caalami ah oo halis ah, gaar ahaan waddamada ay ku nool yihiin dad aad u tiro yar oo aan haysan nidaam caafimaad oo ku filan.
Isagoo ka jawaabaya hoos u dhaca safarka, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in " aysan jirin wax horumar ah oo lagu sameeyo nidaamyada caalamiga ah ee safarka iyo ganacsiga " iyo in " WHO ay ku talinayso in la yareeyo ganacsiga iyo khatarta ".
