Maalintii la soo dhaafay, Tedros ayaa sheegay in Gudoomiyaha Qaramada Midoobay António Guterres uu aqbalay in la siiyo "awood siyaasadeed oo dhan Qaramada Midoobay".
Hay'adda Qaramada Midoobay ee Qaaxada ayaa ka jawaabtay, iyadoo ka hortimidtay jawaabta Qaramada Midoobay, taas oo ay WHO sheegtay inay u xilsaartay inay "siiso jawaab caafimaad oo degdeg ah, isla markaana ay u oggolaato hay'adaha kale inay ku dadaalaan sidii ay uga hortagi lahaayeen dhibaatooyinka baahsan ee bulshada, iyo xayawaanka".
