Enzymka beddelidda angiotensin 2 (ACE2) wuxuu muddo dheer ku jiraa unugyada jirka (fiiri unugyada) unugyada muruqyada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, xididada dhiigga, iyo unugyada neerfaha.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa doorka angiotensin-adeegsiga koronto-qaadista (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo heerka angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta Angiotensin-1-7 taas oo keentay inay noqoto daawo waxtar leh oo daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 sidoo kale waxay u adeegtaa sidii albaab u ah unugyada wadnaha ee coronavirus.
Cudurka bani aadamka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaanaa CAACE2.
Angiotensin-reactive nebula 2 waa zinc-rich metalloenzyme ku jira unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 protein waxa uu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa unugyada kaliya ee ay ku jirto borotiinka xashiishka ee nooca I, kaasoo ah unugyada ugu badan ee uu ka jiro unugyada neefka iyo unugyada kale.
The ACE2 domain oo ah mid ka baxsan unugyada ayaa lagu xiraa unugyada transmembrane iyada oo loo marayo unugyo kala duwan oo loo yaqaan 'sheddase', iyo borotiinada la xiriira ayaa lagu soo saaraa dhiigga, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu sii daayaa unugyada.
ACE2 wuxuu ku jiraa unugyada jirka badankood: ACE2 waxaa ku jira unugyada dhiigga ee unugyada unugyada nooca II ee unugyada jirka, unugyada enterocytes ee unugyada dhiigga, unugyada wadnaha ee wadnaha iyo xididdada xididdada iyo unugyada wadnaha ee muruqyada.
Heerka ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, maskaxda, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
Waxqabadka ACE2 wuxuu ka tarjumayaa sida xakameynta ACE.
ACE wuxuu hormoonka angiotensin I ka dhigaa hormoonka angiotensin II oo xakameynaya xididdada dhiigga.
ACE2 waxay kaloo bedeshaa karboksil-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka soo baxa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ku soo baxa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u gudbin kartaa qaar ka mid ah peptide-yada sida [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa qaabka loo yaqaan 'neutral amino acid receptor SLC6A19' waxayna u badan tahay inay tahay sababta loo yaqaan 'Hartnup syndrome'.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sidii albaab u ah unugyada coronavirus-ka kale, sida HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska keena COVID-19).
Si la mid ah, isku xirnaanta spike S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee unugyada ACE2 ee ku jira unugyada waxay keeni kartaa endocytosis iyo translocation labada fayras ee ku jira unugyada.
