Caddayn badan ayaa soo jeedisay in rhACE2 ay noqon karto dawo waxtar u leh dadka diida nidaamka renin-angiotensin-ka ee caadiga ah (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurada angiotensin II-da la yareeyo. RhACE2 ayaa la baaray tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee lagu daaweynayo cudurka neef-mareenka.
